'''漢斯·李普希'''（{{lang-nl|Hans Lippershey}}，{{bd|1570年||1619年|9月}}{{註|埋葬於1619年9月29日}}），或稱作'''約翰·李普希'''（Johann Lippershey），[[神聖羅馬帝國|德國]]裔[[荷蘭|荷蘭]][[眼鏡|眼鏡製造師]]與發明家。因最早申請望遠鏡的[[專利|專利]]而聞名於世<ref name="false">{{Cite web |url=http://books.google.com/books?id=KAWwzHlDVksC&pg=PA30&dq=Hans+Lippershey+inventor+of+the+telescope.&hl=en&ei=uJKiTJvkIsP6lweQ4dHbAw&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=5&ved=0CD8Q6AEwBDgK#v=onepage&q=Hans%20Lippershey%20inventor%20of%20the%20telescope.&f=false |title=The History of the Telescope, by Henry C. King, page 30 |access-date=2015-09-28 |archive-date=2021-01-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210126064642/https://books.google.com/books?id=KAWwzHlDVksC&pg=PA30&dq=Hans+Lippershey+inventor+of+the+telescope.&hl=en&ei=uJKiTJvkIsP6lweQ4dHbAw&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=5&ved=0CD8Q6AEwBDgK#v=onepage&q=Hans%20Lippershey%20inventor%20of%20the%20telescope.&f=false |dead-url=no }}</ref>，但現時仍未清楚他是否是第一個製造望遠鏡的人。

== 生平 ==
漢斯·李普希在1570年出生[[神聖羅馬帝國|德國]]的[[韋塞爾|韋塞爾]]。他在1594年定居於[[荷蘭|荷蘭]][[澤蘭省|澤蘭省]]的省治[[米德爾堡|米德爾堡]]，同年結婚和在1602年取得荷蘭的公民權。定居米德爾堡期間，他成為了一位鏡片研磨師與[[眼鏡|眼鏡製造師]]。1619年9月，李普希於米德爾堡逝世，年約48至49歲<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.famousinventors.org/hans-lippershey |title=Hans Lippershey |access-date=2015-09-28 |archive-date=2020-09-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200901100742/https://www.famousinventors.org/hans-lippershey |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

=== 發明望遠鏡 ===
{{see also|望遠鏡史}}
漢斯·李普希最著名的事跡是發明望遠鏡，據文字記載，他曾於1608年申請[[折射望遠鏡|折射望遠鏡]]的專利<ref name="false"/><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://books.google.com/books?id=nhgUU3XAytgC&pg=PT58&dq=Hans+Lippershey+inventor+of+the+telescope.&hl=en&ei=jJGiTML7BsKclgfkgfX_Aw&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=2&ved=0CCwQ6AEwATge#v=onepage&q=Hans%20Lippershey%20inventor%20of%20the%20telescope.&f=false |title=Light Years: An Exploration of Mankind's Enduring Fascination with Light By Brian Clegg |access-date=2015-09-28 |archive-date=2017-03-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170310011648/https://books.google.com/books?id=nhgUU3XAytgC&pg=PT58&dq=Hans+Lippershey+inventor+of+the+telescope.&hl=en&ei=jJGiTML7BsKclgfkgfX_Aw&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=2&ved=0CCwQ6AEwATge#v=onepage&q=Hans%20Lippershey%20inventor%20of%20the%20telescope.&f=false |dead-url=no }}</ref>。李普希對[[光學儀器|光學儀器]]的貢獻建基於他原本的工作－眼鏡製造師<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://books.google.com/books?id=2LZZginzib4C&pg=PA62&vq=dutch&dq=intitle:Stargazer+digges+coins&lr=&as_brr=0&source=gbs_search_s&cad=0#PPA55,M1 |title=Fred Watson, ''Stargazer'' (page 55) |access-date=2015-09-28 |archive-date=2017-03-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170310011405/https://books.google.com/books?id=2LZZginzib4C&pg=PA62&vq=dutch&dq=intitle:Stargazer+digges+coins&lr=&as_brr=0&source=gbs_search_s&cad=0#PPA55,M1 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，這是一個始源於十三世紀意大利[[威尼斯|威尼斯]]和[[佛羅倫斯|佛羅倫斯]]的行業<ref name="Swain">{{Cite web |url=http://galileo.rice.edu/sci/instruments/telescope.html |title=galileo.rice.edu The Galileo Project > Science > The Telescope by Al Van Helden |accessdate=2015-09-28 |archive-date=2020-05-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200509061206/http://galileo.rice.edu/sci/instruments/telescope.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，之後擴展至荷蘭和德國<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://books.google.co.uk/books?hl=en&lr=&id=KAWwzHlDVksC&oi=fnd&pg=PR1&dq=alhazen+and+the+telescope&ots=0GOT5dCTU8&sig=U-uj1p9TvkAW12XFz8mkfI6TWMg#PPA27,M1 |title=''The History of the Telescope'' By Henry C. King, page 27, "''(spectacles) invention, an important step in the history of the telescope''" |accessdate=2015-09-28 |archive-date=2017-09-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170910130220/https://books.google.co.uk/books?hl=en&lr=&id=KAWwzHlDVksC&oi=fnd&pg=PR1&dq=alhazen+and+the+telescope&ots=0GOT5dCTU8&sig=U-uj1p9TvkAW12XFz8mkfI6TWMg#PPA27,M1 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

李普希於1608年10月2日向[[荷蘭國會|荷蘭國會]]提交對其發現的「能看到很遠的地方，好像它們就在你附近一樣的東西」的專利申請<ref name="telescopes">{{Cite web |url=http://www.bo.astro.it/dip/Museum/english/can_int.html |title=Osservatorio Astronomico di Bologna - TELESCOPES |accessdate=2015-09-28 |archive-date=2017-11-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171113112900/http://www.bo.astro.it/dip/Museum/english/can_int.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，同時另一眼鏡製造師{{link-en|雅各·梅提斯|Jacob Metius}}也要求擁有望遠鏡的所有權，最終雙方都未能取得專利<ref name="Swain"/>。雖然如此，李普希還是因其設計的望遠鏡複製品而從荷蘭政府中獲得豐富的報酬。

在[[大城王國|大城王國]]國王{{link-en|厄加陀沙拉|Ekathotsarot}}寫給大城王國駐荷蘭大使館的書信《由暹羅國王寫給[[拿騷的毛里茨|莫里斯親王]]閣下，於1608年9月10日送抵[[海牙|海牙]]》的最後特別表揚漢斯·李普希。該書信發行於同年10月並分發到整個歐洲，引起許多科學家的關注，其中包括{{link-en|保洛·薩爾皮|Paolo Sarpi}}、[[托馬斯·哈里奧特|托馬斯·哈里奧特]]和[[伽利略·伽利萊|伽利略·伽利萊]]。其中伽利略自製並改良-{了}-望遠鏡，將其用於天文觀察<ref>Van Helden ([[#Reference-vanhelden-1977|1977]], p.40; [[#Reference-vanhelden-1985|1985]], [http://books.google.com/books?id=L-yb7GX9mQIC&pg=PA65 p.65] {{Wayback|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=L-yb7GX9mQIC&pg=PA65 |date=20170310170635 }}), Stillman Drake ([[#Reference-Drake-1978|1978]],  [http://books.google.com/books?id=OwOlRPbrZeQC&pg=PA138 p.138] {{Wayback|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=OwOlRPbrZeQC&pg=PA138 |date=20170310002148 }})</ref>。

關於李普希怎樣發明望遠鏡有幾個版本。其中一個版本是有2個小孩在玩李普希店裡的[[透鏡|透鏡]]，並告訴他怎樣看到遠處的[[風向標|風向標]]。其他則包括從他徒弟口中得知或抄襲別人的點子<ref name=corner>{{Cite web |url=http://books.google.com/books?id=PIzziChYQvoC&pg=PA326&dq=hans+lippershey+children&hl=en&ei=IY6eTNDnHYG8lQfEpb3lCg&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=9&ved=0CE8Q6AEwCA#v=onepage&q=hans%20lippershey%20children&f=false |title=A people's history of science: miners, midwives, and "low mechanicks" By Clifford D. Conner |access-date=2015-09-28 |archive-date=2021-03-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308043353/https://books.google.com/books?id=PIzziChYQvoC&pg=PA326&dq=hans+lippershey+children&hl=en&ei=IY6eTNDnHYG8lQfEpb3lCg&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=9&ved=0CE8Q6AEwCA#v=onepage&q=hans%20lippershey%20children&f=false |dead-url=no }}</ref>。李普希最初製作的望遠鏡由2個[[凸透鏡|凸透鏡]]（其中一個是[[物鏡|物鏡]]）和1個[[接目鏡|目鏡]]組成<ref name=corner/>。這款後來被希臘科學家[[喬瓦尼·德米西亞尼|喬瓦尼·德米西亞尼]]命名為「荷蘭透視望遠鏡」的望遠鏡有著3X的[[望遠鏡放大倍數|倍率]]。

